  {
    "hotel_id": "430923",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/hoian-nostalgia-hotel-spa/hotel/hoi-an-vn.html",
    "name": "Hoian Nostalgia Hotel & Spa",
    "detail": "The welcome we got was extremely underwhelming. A grumpy receptionist who seemed completely disinterested in our arrival set the tone of our stay unfortunately. The breakfast staff were the only real positive here. They were friendly and breakfast was good. The rooms were bizarrely dark (maybe an attempt to hide the dust/ grubby state of the room) The pool should have been nice, but was over chlorinated and as the hotel is right next to a noisy/ dusty road not that pleasant in reality. The final negative is that the bed was really uncomfortable. A month in vietnam has us used to harder than normal beds but this was so hard that it prevented us both from sleeping. Usually I am hesitant to write such a negative review, but for the price we paid we were very disappointed with our experience here and have since had better and cheaper accommodation in Hoi An. ",
